  Web Statistics DB Server aka : mooWApp

  Typical usage :
  ---------------
  Count visits for certains URLs each day and let the stats be accessible thru
  an Intranet.

  Advantages :
  ------------
  - No modification of apps.
  - Administrators can monitor specific pages.
  - RoundRobin mecanism to keep a small DB

  V0.1: 
  -----
  a. First alpha version running on BerkeleyDB and Mongoose
  	
===============================================================================
  BE CAREFULL NOT TO USE THIS APP FOR RIGHT NOW: DEVELOPPMENT IN PROGRESS	
